The paper discusses the integration of information transfer and power transfer in wireless communication systems, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The paper also discusses the use of electromagnetic waves for power transfer, which falls under the category of electromagnetics (cs.EM). The paper also discusses the use of medium access control and network protocols, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the use of resource allocation, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
